{"tid":891022,"cid":9,"subCid":0,"title":"whatsapp真係世界垃圾 backup問題","createTime":"2018-11-05T19:27:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-10T11:19:15.000Z","uid":86086,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"1fdfe09255632c73ae68b476e3a496b31af09fe1","tid":891022,"uid":86086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T19:27:27.000Z","msg":"簡單黎講<br />\n我唔小心del左whatsapp<br />\n得番一個月前backup落既whatsapp記錄<br />\n我唔小心del左 裝番 禁錯左backup(咩都冇)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nIcloud自動將我whatsapp backup update左最新咩都冇既<br />\n呢家點restore都係空白<br />\n明明一個月前既backup 有好多對話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我10月1號backup左既whatsapp係icloud到<br />\n我11月1號bakcup錯左(咩都冇既)<br />\n係咪冇可能搵番10月1號果陣既backup檔<br />\n上網有d recover軟件 收錢唔係問題<br />\n都冇撚用 check到我1月1號既backup呀 但都down唔撚到落黎<br />\n<br />\n有冇巴絲有咩諗法 好重要 有客果d資料"},{"pid":"6af615932466f9904498546e95f61a5f36d42725","tid":891022,"uid":86086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T19:29:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67962766d93c52565bffedefd0daf6215a8959ab","tid":891022,"uid":86086,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T19:30:58.000Z","msg":"訓前一推算了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9474e8948da583f28c67448ea4245eea5e535c0a","tid":891022,"uid":86086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T19:36:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"229e47a2ba5321bfe88c4b4989183858bad39f58","tid":891022,"uid":33874,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T19:38:49.000Z","msg":"Android都仲有機<br />\nIphone你可以訓先"},{"pid":"42b84efbd297fb06f199442bf5360073926d9cd1","tid":891022,"uid":86086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"229e47a2ba5321bfe88c4b4989183858bad39f58","tid":891022,"uid":33874,"like":1